name: RYANAIR 737-800 | LONDON STANSTED - CITY OF DERRY
description:
Fly with me to City of Derry Airport in Northern Ireland, on a Ryanair 737-800 from Stansted. 

Ryanair are the only carrier to serve Derry, and fares are low. This was booked for Â£10.99 all in; no bag in the hold and it would have been even cheaper had I not wanted to pick a window seat!

I take the early departure, on a crisp autumn morning. Enjoy the report, and don't forget to subscribe!
